value.name: Choosing files to download for Drivers and Firmware : Windows10 - reddit
value.snippet: First things first: drivers and firmware should be two separate things and are never downloaded or installed together. Then, look at the first numbers in the file name, Win10_18362 is clearly more recent than Win10_16299. Plus, if the drivers are official you should see some kind of description around their name. level 2. Op · 2 yr. ago.
